title: Hotel Maruthi Inn
subTitle: హోటల్ మారుతీ ఇన్న్
description: Straightforward rooms with air conditioners in a budget hotel with a rooftop restaurant.
address: 5-180/1/A , opposite Vijaya high school , manjulapur, Nirmal, Telangana 504106, India
hotelDescription:
Set on National Highway 61, this down-to-earth budget hotel is 3 km from Syam Ghad Fort and 19 km from Pala Waagu waterfall.
 Simply decorated rooms provide flat-screen TVs, ceiling fans and air conditioners, as well as en suite wet rooms. Some offer views of a nearby lake.
 Amenities include parking and Wi-Fi, plus an informal rooftop restaurant. Banquet facilities are available.
